StoredProcedureOraclev10g.name: GETTUTORSTUDENT
StoredProcedureOraclev10g.source: CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE GRUPO10.GETTUTORSTUDENT(cTutorStudent OUT SYS_REFCURSOR)&lt;br/&gt;IS&lt;br/&gt;BEGIN&lt;br/&gt; OPEN cTutorStudent FOR &lt;br/&gt; SELECT TutorStudent_table.idPerson, TutorStudent_table.surname, TutorStudent_table.firstName, &lt;br/&gt; TutorStudent_table.title, TutorStudent_table.address, TutorStudent_table.phone, TutorStudent_table.postcode,&lt;br/&gt; TutorStudent_table.campusLocation, TutorStudent_table.year, TutorStudent_table.numberHours, TutorStudent_table.rate&lt;br/&gt; FROM TutorStudent_table;&lt;br/&gt;END getTutorStudent;
